---
/**
 * NetworkingSection.astro — Sprint 2
 * Breakout rooms / icebreaker section.
 */
---

<section class="py-16 px-6 bg-[#F7F4EF]" id="breakout">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
    <div class="text-[.73rem] font-bold tracking-[.15em] uppercase text-orange mb-2">
      Momento de Conexão
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.7rem,4vw,2.5rem)] font-extrabold leading-tight mb-10">
      Breakout Rooms
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal to-navy text-white rounded-3xl p-10 text-center max-w-[700px] mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-[1.4rem] font-extrabold mb-3">🎯 Pergunta Quebra-Gelo</h3>
      <div class="text-[1.15rem] italic text-white/85 bg-black/15 p-5 rounded-2xl my-5
                  border-l-4 border-orange">
        "Qual o maior impacto que a IA já causou no seu trabalho até hoje?"
      </div>
      <p class="text-[.88rem] opacity-80">
        Apresente-se, responda e descubra com quem quer trabalhar.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
